t for get anything you want to see on here let jade know <!-- s:) --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon_e_smile.gif\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Smile\" /><!-- s:) -->\n\nfeel free to inbox me in game or on here i do come and login every morning to check my mail <!-- s:) --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon_e_smile.gif\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Smile\" /><!-- s:) -->\nand any messages would be great.. its getting rather boring now looking at the same 4 walls for aprox 6 weeks and it looks like be another 4 week before i can think about work <!-- s:( --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon_e_sad.gif\" alt=\":(\" title=\"Sad\" /><!-- s:( -->\n\nwell the sun is coming up think its gonna be another hot 1 so im going to take my self out side and listen to some tunes, got a lovely blowup  bed for out to lie on <!-- s:) --><img src=\"{SMILIES_PATH}/icon_e_smile.gif\" alt=\":)\" title=\"Smile\" /><!-- s:) -->\n\nSee you soon\n\nRegards\nEpidemic\n ( Martin )', '9cc24b5eec6444f53bdab9309f1b0a5f', 0, '', 'rjqqzbuu', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),(22, 2, 21, 62, 0, '86.160.249.75', 1375308154, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Welcome to the new CCA Forums!', 'oi oi', 'c9c7cf7a1c4aef64f0290af0a42b19ad', 0, '', '3lqjxe03', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),(9, 6, 0, 2, 0, '86.185.78.168', 1373556733, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '[Important] - Apply to your Usergroup!', 'Hey all,\n\nIf you are not in the correct Usergroup you may apply to join one here: [url:1xb0wkb1]http&#58;//crimson-alliance&#46;com/forum/ucp&#46;php?i=176[/url:1xb0wkb1]\n\nAfter you have applied, please give time for an admin to check your application, and your group will be updated as soon as possible.\n\nThank you,\nJade', 'b3f89848c89820ad578130a5ce64dd7d', 0, 'EA==', '1xb0wkb1', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0),(10, 7, 24, 2, 0, '86.185.78.168', 1373575416, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '[Raids] - Subscribe to Me!', 'Subscribe for notifications if you would like to be notified via email each time a raid is posted.\n\nIf you don\'t subscribe, you will still receive a forum PM if the event poster requests it.\n\nThanks,\nJade', '7f9ac56d7752883bf398c52b8204f3b7', 0, '', '1wa4ae0m', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0);

